{"tid":61440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[直播]毒撚11日廣島之行","createTime":"2016-12-31T08:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T16:32:36.000Z","uid":8105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca427954f817e97f607946516828c61f0679dcaf","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的我就想去廣島好耐<br />\n之前見到hkexpress有平機票就狗衝左<br />\nDAY1&amp;2 宮島<br />\nDay3&amp;4 廣島市內<br />\nDay4 吳市<br />\nDay6 岡山<br />\nDay7 倉蔽<br />\nDay8 岩國<br />\nDay9 免島<br />\nDay10 博多<br />\nDay 11 hea<br />\n<br />\n以上行程好大可能改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說我10晚都係住同一間hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚就會係宮島倒數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後搵個地方坐到朝早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/164249_d5bbb47ed0965580aad1e4929bff09e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F164249_d5bbb47ed0965580aad1e4929bff09e1.jpg&h=4b27347f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV6gy6JHqab9S7oc4ZcQae62NfaKLNUz48xyn9bWxWQA6?filename=x52566g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx52566g.jpg&h=d519ead7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVeRs4JaL9SZZMsJLUeNFSdAFn8i6DqFXCRdCYD9jnfQo?filename=p745TBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp745TBM.jpg&h=79cadc40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/164310_b5b7fe64b0c862a40960f4b35c06bf22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F164310_b5b7fe64b0c862a40960f4b35c06bf22.jpg&h=d81dd509&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http