\n<br />\n冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估去非洲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一個人去就過海關好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見佢十個有九個都check D一個人個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要搜身又要攞曬d野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a1dab88835086e0dcca0ad37db40b53a182b1e","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVeRs4JaL9SZZMsJLUeNFSdAFn8i6DqFXCRdCYD9jnfQo?filename=p745TBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp745TBM.jpg&h=79cadc40&s={SIZE}\" />)</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撮影禁止</span><br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我見入境個到有所以冇影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真心唔知呢到都唔影得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f67badfd7fb2cacd04065916a6937f32455a28","tid":61440,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/182600_658e27033afbd002f2edd8366228fea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F182600_658e27033afbd002f2edd8366228fea0.jpg&h=15492681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲未整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63dd07e59d8549c354f944a696382068f85997b","tid":61440,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockq