<blockquote>我諗緊好唔好翻hostel訓下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間hostel係邊?咁晚仲有船?"},{"pid":"0c20874abefcaafc4621f0419c8d6a914c36e9f7","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗緊好唔好翻hostel訓下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間hostel係邊?咁晚仲有船?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係翻廣島站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n翻左去就睇唔到日出同埋要俾多幾千yen車錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日通宵"},{"pid":"8cb1885a3eed89d9877df9e23adfa7c4267f02c4","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"最後都係決定翻去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好涷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾多1000&yen;交通費先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁搞法可能day 11先至日頭再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a996d404989e2e00c9f0150bc7fa4c2b6c0640","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTU8gLwtjNVhTdujE5cSAJcj1YyuhUDX5Khuhqf2Ee8Rc?filename=ey0q34P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fey0q34P.jpg&h=ee1bc3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去個時係撘JR<br />\n今次試下另外一間<br />\n同樣價錢JR更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2cbe661df34764a84071fe2a4c9f678c55b165","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後都係決定翻去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好涷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾多1000&yen;交通費先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁搞法可能day 11先至日頭再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我個日個pass仲未到期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082c063ee2dadfcdc3e226d198c7ec7a9e1bbd53","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"等車翻去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbJjGeZvLsgsSX3TcbEV8j9PXE3oK2L6XcvoDxd2HA6E?filename=Uz1G7yt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUz1G7yt.jpg&h=f8770e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭先見到班車站人員係到派野<br />\n但就係冇派俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又唔好意思行埋去攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你原來係暖包黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早知攞啦屌"},{"pid":"52a8121c966210db7ad18b6a81ac5b4061c730a0","tid":61440,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/01/005610_1a60e6162409131a9784d6269ea81e5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/